longBusinessSummary: Interact-TV, Inc. operates as a multifaceted multi-media development company. It primarily develops film and radio digital production and broadcasting platforms. The company operates Internet TV and radio channels. It also provides full service distribution and music services for bands and other labels; develops and distributes video game software products; and publishes and distributes books. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Wilmington, Delaware.
